// /peticion-de-mano (CA), /es/peticion-de-mano (ES), /en/peticion-de-mano (EN).
//
// Audience overlap with brides-to-be is essentially zero (the proposal
// happens months before any wedding-photographer search), so this is
// its own page rather than a section on the home. Schema.org Service
// + FAQPage + Breadcrumb let Google rank it for "fotograf petició de mà
// Tarragona" / "fotógrafo pedida mano Tarragona" / "proposal photographer
// Tarragona" — niches with low competition.
//
// All copy is keyed by `lang`. CA stays the default voice (warm,
// local). ES is a tighter Spanish; EN leans into the foreign-traveler
// angle since that's the segment most likely to read it.

